    <item>
      <title>奥特曼基础设施计划计划在美国投资数百亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/altman-infrastructure-plan-aims-to-spend-tens-of-billions-in-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，OpenAI 首席执行官 Sam Altman 大规模建设人工智能所需的机器和系统的计划正逐渐清晰，首先在美国各州开展的一项计划预计将耗资数百亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/altman-infrastructure-plan-aims-to-spend-tens-of-billions-in-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 22:06:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克的 Starlink 计划让步，同意在巴西阻止 X 项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/musk-s-starlink-backs-down-vows-to-comply-and-block-x-in-brazil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克的卫星互联网提供商 Starlink 改变了方针，表示将遵守巴西最高法院的命令，阻止拉丁美洲最大的国家访问这位亿万富翁的社交网络 X。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/musk-s-starlink-backs-down-vows-to-comply-and-block-x-in-brazil</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 21:33:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾和中国的科技紧张局势，X 在巴西停工 | 彭博科技</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-03/taiwan-and-china-tech-tensions-x-goes-dark-in-brazil-bloomberg-technology</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的 Caroline Hyde 和 Ed Ludlow 详细分析了台湾为何指责中国非法从其科技公司挖走人才。此外，巴西法官确认在全国范围内停职 X，大型科技公司的亏损扩大至 2%。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-03/taiwan-and-china-tech-tensions-x-goes-dark-in-brazil-bloomberg-technology</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 21:05:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>司法部公布社交媒体战略以打击外国威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/us-vows-no-pre-election-pressure-on-meta-x-to-fight-foreign-meddling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在有指控称社交媒体平台此前受到胁迫后，当政府分享有关外国对国家安全或选举构成威胁的信息时，美国司法部不会向社交媒体公司施压，要求其删除或屏蔽内容。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/us-vows-no-pre-election-pressure-on-meta-x-to-fight-foreign-meddling</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 21:05:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Snap 首席执行官在股价下跌期间召集员工关注广告业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/snap-ceo-spiegel-rallies-workers-on-ad-business-amid-stock-drop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Snap Inc. 首席执行官埃文·斯皮格尔 (Evan Spiegel) 试图在股价今年下跌 48% 的情况下团结员工，他在一封内部信中告诉员工，公司有望实现创纪录的年收入，并将继续推进增强现实业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/snap-ceo-spiegel-rallies-workers-on-ad-business-amid-stock-drop</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 21:01:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nvidia 在不断升级的反垄断调查中收到美国司法部传票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/nvidia-gets-doj-subpoena-in-escalating-antitrust-investigation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部向英伟达公司和其他公司发出传票，寻找该芯片制造商违反反垄断法的证据，这是其对这家人工智能处理器主要供应商的调查升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/nvidia-gets-doj-subpoena-in-escalating-antitrust-investigation</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 20:24:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>DirecTV 为丢失迪士尼频道的用户提供 20 美元退款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/directv-offers-customers-20-refund-for-lost-disney-channels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[DirecTV 将向其用户提供 20 美元的退款，以弥补 ESPN、ABC 和华特迪士尼公司旗下其他频道的转播损失，这凸显了两家公司在谈判新合同时涉及的金额之巨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/directv-offers-customers-20-refund-for-lost-disney-channels</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 19:10:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能担忧导致股价下跌，英伟达市值暴跌 2790 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/nvidia-s-240-billion-swoon-leads-rout-in-semiconductor-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[四周前，在全球逃离风险资产的浪潮中，美国股市暴跌。随后，两名芯片制造商的行业分析师再次引发人们对人工智能狂热过度的担忧，引发了又一轮股票抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/nvidia-s-240-billion-swoon-leads-rout-in-semiconductor-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 16:27:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国比亚迪暂停墨西哥工厂建设计划直至美国大选结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/china-s-byd-said-to-pause-mexico-plant-until-after-us-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，中国最大的电动汽车制造商比亚迪股份有限公司至少要在美国大选之后才会宣布在墨西哥投资大型工厂，因为美国政策的变化迫使全球企业进入观望模式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/china-s-byd-said-to-pause-mexico-plant-until-after-us-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 14:14:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
